@startuml
title Deterministic Distributed Transaction State Machine

[*] --> CREATED

CREATED --> VALIDATED : validation_success
CREATED --> FAILED : validation_failed

VALIDATED --> DEBIT_IN_PROGRESS : initiate_debit

DEBIT_IN_PROGRESS --> DEBIT_SUCCESS : debit_confirmed
DEBIT_IN_PROGRESS --> FAILED : debit_failed_or_unresolved_timeout

DEBIT_SUCCESS --> CREDIT_IN_PROGRESS : initiate_credit

CREDIT_IN_PROGRESS --> SUCCESS : credit_confirmed
CREDIT_IN_PROGRESS --> COMPENSATION_IN_PROGRESS : credit_failed_or_unresolved_timeout

COMPENSATION_IN_PROGRESS --> COMPENSATED : reverse_debit_confirmed

SUCCESS --> [*]
FAILED --> [*]
COMPENSATED --> [*]

note right of FAILED
Terminal when debit has not completed successfully.
end note

note right of COMPENSATED
Terminal when debit succeeded but credit failed,
and reverse debit succeeded.
end note

@enduml
